<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-cn">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<title>只做专场人才拍卖 - 实力拍</title>
	<meta name="keywords" content="实力拍, 人才拍卖">
	<meta name="description" content="实力拍是深圳市红领巾网络科技有限公司旗下的项目">
	<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
	<meta name="renderer" content="webkit|ie-comp|ie-stand">
	<meta http-equiv="Cache-Control" content="no-cache, no-store, must-revalidate">
	<meta http-equiv="Pragma" content="no-cache">
	<meta http-equiv="Expires" content="0">
	<link rel="shortcut icon" href="../css/img/logo_ico.ico">
	<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../css/common/normalize.css">
	<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../css/common/global.css">
	<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../css/common/compslt.css">
	
	<!-- <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../css/dist/master.min.css">
	<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../css/dist/compslt.min.css"> -->
	
	<!--[if lt IE 9]>
      <script src="../js/common/html5.min.js"></script>
      <script src="../js/common/respond.min.js"></script>
    <![endif]-->
    
	<script src="../js/common/require_config.js" defer="true"></script>
	<script data-main="../js/controller/compslt" src="../js/common/require.min.js" defer="true"></script>
	<!-- <script type="text/javascript" src="js/controller/dist/compslt-built.min.js" defer="true"></script> -->
</head>
<body>
	<div class="viewport">
		<div id="header" ng-include src="'../views/header.html'" ng-controller="headerCtrl" ng-init="getUserInfo()"></div>
		<div id="main" ng-controller="sltCtrl">
			<div class="slt-wrap box-shadow" ng-init="getCompList()">
				<div class="nav-warp">
	  				<div class="tab-item slt">
	  					<div class="tab-step">1</div>
	  					<div class="tab-text">选择公司</div>
	  				</div>
	  				<div class="line"></div>
	  				<div class="tab-item">
	  					<div class="tab-step">2</div>
	  					<div class="tab-text">基本信息</div>
	  				</div>
  				</div>
  				
  				<div class="box-item">
					<div class="comp-warp">
		  				<div class="item-title">
		  					<span><i>*</i> 根据您填写的公司邮箱<a ng-click="backRegister()">（修改邮箱地址）</a>，请选择您所在的公司名称：</span>
		  				</div>
		  				<div class="con-slt" ng-class="{true: 'mgn-1'}[(queryList.length > 0)]" ng-if="!editStatus">
		  					<div class="comp-list">
		  						<div ng-repeat="item in queryList">
		  							<a class="com-name" target="_blank" ng-href="/base/chome{{item.companyId}}.html" ng-bind="item.name"></a>
		  							<span class="com-opt" ng-click="useExistCompany(item.companyId)">使用这个公司的名称和信息</span>
		  						</div>
		  					</div>			
		  				</div>
		  				<div class="btn-group" ng-if="!editStatus">
  							<button class="btn" ng-click="editComp(1)">创建新公司</button>
  						</div>
						<div class="con-add" ng-if="editStatus">
		  					<div><input type="text" id="comp_info" ng-model="compInfo.companyName" ng-change="_clearTip()" placeholder="请输入公司名称"></div>
							<div class="err-wrap">
								<label id="comp_info_tip" class="ico-invalid"></label>
							</div>	  					
		  					<div class="">
		  						<button ng-class="{'true': 'active'}[(compInfo.companyName.length > 0)]" ng-click="addCompany()">提交</button>
		  					</div>
		  				</div>		  				
		  			</div>				
  				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div id="footer" ng-include src="'../views/footer.html'"></div>
	</div>
</body>
</html>
